{"tid":1883781,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有無巴絲打將謝霆鋒首黃 改一改","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T08:55:26.000Z","uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b329ef1686bee14ece6d15154ccb66fcb4efaf9","tid":1883781,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒 <br />\n<br />\n黃<br />\n<br />\n作詞：周耀輝<br />\n作曲：謝霆鋒<br />\n<br />\n黃泥湧出某一種氣力　煉成大地就要闖蕩<br />\n黃泉顯出五千種太極　聚成命運就稱作東方<br />\n<br />\n黃銅刻出某一種偶像　唸成大事在我心臟<br />\n黃皮長出五千種漂亮　鍍成現在讓我出汗<br />\n<br />\n＊從玄黃　取一把火　要靠我來點旺<br />\n　閻羅王　都不敢講　那怕世代太動盪<br />\n<br />\n＃一身黃　千種狂　世界越變要夠膽闖<br />\n　原來新生黃　想張狂　千古等著我演出這片黃<br />\n<br />\n△黃蓮開出某一種故事　譯成二字就叫希望 <br />\n　黃皮長出五千種正義　鍍成現在讓我出汗<br />\n<br />\nRepeat ＊,＃<br />\n<br />\nRap:<br />\n天下哪有地方看不到黃色的臉　鮮紅色的血　流在<span style=\"color: red;\">十三億的人<br />\n你說這是我的憤怒　我說這是我的態度<br />\n奮不顧身　勇往直前　只有我們中國人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRepeat △<br />\n<br />\n一身黃　千種狂　我有我的新武裝<br />\n就讓一身黃　撐起風浪　我作我的男兒漢"},{"pid":"2695cf0ee45297aa9de97d3708754de2a063e221","tid":1883781,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a17a4e48b18700e5435fedbfea1eeb6a02d1f56","tid":1883781,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84889e8f6d00603479103bd749f3947ba0d62a2f","tid":1883781,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"其實首歌同曲幾正 改改歌詞就幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cecb7d3539d9b2dd5149ca76d1652b62c223d17","tid":1883781,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"請出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff47